						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Rājanārāyaṇa Sambuvarāya. Year 13: A.D. 1350.</hi></p>						

						<p>(<hi rend="italic">Kumbha, śu., 13</hi>, Friday, <hi rend="italic">Uttirāḍam</hi> (irregular) = A.D. 1350.)</p>						

						<p>Built in at the end. Seems to record a <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> gift of 2 <hi rend="italic">vēlis</hi> of land at Vittūr, the northern hamlet of Madhurāntaka-chaturvēdimaṅgalam, a village in Kaḷattūrk-kōṭṭam of Jayaṅkoṇḍachōḻa-maṇḍalam for undertaking repairs and services in the temple. Mentions the land measure <hi rend="italic">nāḍaḷavu-kōl.</hi></p>						

